These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, indonesian, dutch, french
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the french is between the indian and the indonesian##2
3. the french is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | indian | french | indonesian | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pepper, watermelon, peach
1. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating pepper is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pepper | grapes | peach | watermelon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, animation, action, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
2. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching action movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | action | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, cricket, cycling
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
2. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | swimming | skiing | cycling | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon, tennis, golf
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | golf | rugby | tennis | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, nigerian, mexican
1. the polish is on the far right##1
2. the polish is on the left or right of the mexican##3
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | german | mexican | polish |

