.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, trike, bus
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | trike | bike | bus | helicopter |

