1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | mirinda | juice |

