2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | basketball | golf | snowboarding | skateboarding |

